  "texts": [
    "The feature f 2 i is mapped from single-atom representation and pair-atom representations g 0 ij; h ij by a multiple-layer structure,",
    "where the single-and pair-atom representations are updated by repformer (representation-transformer) layers.",
    "The repformer is designed in a way that the input and output representations share the shape dimension, thus they are stacked 12 times.",
    "The \"∘\" in Eq.",
    "(10) thus denotes the layer composition (or mathematically the function composition)."
  ],
